title: Diners Drive-Ins Dives S01E01-S20E05 COMPLETE MP4 AAC theMDR
description:
This is the COMPLETE Series (as of today) of Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives.  

As per the original airings:
Seasons 1-10 are 480p 4:3* (640x480, H264 MP4, 128mpbs AAC) 
Seasons 11-20 are 720p 16:9 (1280x720, H264 MP4, 128mpbs AAC)

Special thanks to SoFRiTo, whose collection I used as a starting point, transcoding most of them for this one.  I filled in the rest that were missing via separate downloads, recordings, etc.

*I was missing S03E13, which was recently aired in "modified" Widescreen (part stretched and part cropped), so I settled on 1:66 as the ratio.   Enjoy!

theMDR = The Media Done Right
